Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(825,600}{\fad(500,0}第15話         如  果  能  回  到  那  天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿腐臭的沼澤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是讓人喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快和他們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這片沼澤  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的攻擊是不起作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是各種死之符號與俗世相互交融的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你們生者所能夠理解的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會出來個什麼樣的冥鬥士呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跳出來個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為了戰鬥而出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來給予你心底渴望的 想要的東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 這就是你渴望的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是給予進入這片森林的人的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砥草  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…幻覺來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 對不起 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我 讓你背負了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那麼漂亮的皮膚 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都刺上刺青了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他們在去往山腳的村子的途中 掉落山崖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史昂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸天國了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙親和砥草  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是爸爸和媽媽的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟砥草一個人 也許是因為掉到了更深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能找到遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在這嘉米爾之村也是舉足輕重的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必會有傳承之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我們一族的血脈就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定由我來繼承了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我的夢想是成為您這樣的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜的聖鬥士專程露面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不只是為了回鄉歸省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定也從長老那裡聽說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過200多年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,108顆魔星又一次被釋放到了這片大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天前 教皇塞奇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感覺到在這嘉米爾有不祥的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嘉米爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的這條圍巾 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也會在出嫁時帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砥草 你還活著嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼你會穿著冥衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是冥鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:19.02,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈奴曼，印度史詩《羅摩衍那》的神猴，擁有四張臉和八支手， 解救阿逾陀國王子羅摩之妻悉多，與羅剎惡魔羅波那大戰。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名天巧星 哈奴曼（Hanuman）的砥草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 為什麼你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達拿都斯大人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說 只要成為冥鬥士 就會給予你永恆的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 獻上你的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代價？ 難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很敏銳啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深愛之人的死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把爸爸和媽媽給…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到姐姐你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你嗎 砥草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉米爾的不祥的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何如此渴求不死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜奪走深愛之人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想變得和姐姐你一樣強大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不死的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用害怕死亡的恐懼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能超越姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才選擇了成為冥鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被冥王軍給利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 對於已被達拿都斯影響的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼都是白搭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我不能放過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜的聖鬥士 白羊座的黃金聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是何等貨色 我也想見識見識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧 砥草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 冥鬥士 天巧星的哈奴曼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的招數我都看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直都在你身邊看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你卻不知道 成為冥鬥士後的我 現在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積屍氣如意靈臨（Praesepe Departed Soul Summoning）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史昂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白羊座的黃金聖衣還挺脆弱啊 史昂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能允許你污蔑史昂大人！  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砥草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 連戰士都不是的姐姐你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為戰士的血脈由冥鬥士的我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冥界 永遠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這血脈和家紋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還是全部都帶去地獄才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的血 刻在我的身軀上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和那些殺了摯愛之人也無動於衷的冥鬥士們一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要背負那麼重的罪孽 讓葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的強大 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的堅定緊緊地抓住了姐姐的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為她憧憬的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且讓姐姐變成了離我越來越遠的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在的我比你更強大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓你阻礙我  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況 區區一個雅典娜的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的使命明確了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從冥王軍手中保護我的故鄉嘉米爾  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積屍氣如意靈臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星屑旋轉功(Stardust Revolution)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不可能  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是黃金聖鬥士的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砥草  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在故鄉的土地上安靜地睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會染上血的 會弄髒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我是戰士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去 好想回嘉米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砥草…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能把這傢伙從死亡之中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砥草
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 想要救你弟弟 也不是沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這傢伙殺掉 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他的生命移給你弟弟就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶…耶人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可猶豫的 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定還想再一次和弟弟一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在故鄉的大地上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,險峻的岩山和廣闊的天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能和你 再次回到那裡 該有多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起回去吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回嘉米爾 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須結束這場聖戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體竟然支離破碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那塊布靠我小小的念力就能自由運動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並能根據小宇宙的燃燒程度做出反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產生熱量和風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來變得容易粉碎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢舞裳閃腳（Beautiful Flashing Kicks）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連親弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了戰鬥 都能拋棄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我看上去很冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這就是我的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為選擇必然伴隨著後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘸著弟弟的血 把家紋紋在了這個手臂上 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同砥草的靈魂一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我今後作為一名戰士戰鬥到底的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深地刻在了上面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要保護的東西 我也會去保護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將嘉米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這大地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負於自己纖細的雙肩的那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要同天馬和耶人一起守護她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼陰森恐怖的森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人居然都走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬 讓葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我自己能不能保住小命才是問題啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃腐肉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是雅典娜的聖鬥士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 它居然還會說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待 你會是什麼味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓這種傢伙吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這算是在攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱爆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也敢腆著臉闖進這森林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想來到 居然會來這種破地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連變成腐肉被吞的價值也沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽小鬼太礙眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把聖衣扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經不是戰士了 留他何用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是雅典娜的聖鬥士嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和嬰兒沒什麼兩樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然愚弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 我對聖鬥士的使命之類的沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是憧憬當個英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管打幾次 耶人哥你肯定不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 聽好了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽米德根姐說了 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遙遠的異國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著身穿亮閃閃的金啊銀啊的鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了女神而戰鬥的戰士對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以我有一天也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走出這個村子 成為英雄對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經聽煩啦了 你這話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶人 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米德根姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就倒下了 不停地說胡話 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨說些不知所以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王要復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近也有魔星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶她去看醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去有醫生的村鎮 必須翻越好幾座山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我耶人大人吧  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要成為英雄的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 姐姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 離村鎮不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道有外國進攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你幹的嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了救姐姐 好不容易才到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們姐弟的小命也要就此畫上句號了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來要成為英雄的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連姐姐一個人都保護不了 怎麼說的過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去另一個世界做白日夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天蠍座的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說大話的小鬼  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要當英雄 可是會經常受重傷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金的鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憑嘴說 你就會有一腔熱血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命這東西 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是停滯不前 總有一天會消失完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直像你現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子都不會變成你想要的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子都不會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了吧 米德根姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛渾身是傷的背著姐姐回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說什麼我要成為英雄 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑出去以後就一直沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我好不容易得到的獨角獸座聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和天馬和讓葉一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了雅典娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜的聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨角獸飛奔(Unicorn Gallop)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的流星拳居然會被彈回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多少次都是一樣的 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你把小宇宙提升到多高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這些小可愛在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的拳對我都是不起作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些蒼蠅 把我的流星拳給…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭倦做你的對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把皮膚咬破…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他吃的連屍體都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條圍巾是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶人 讓葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然來了這麼多生者…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們溼熱的汗水 血和呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不純潔最令我討厭了  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我都交給僕人們了  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們居然都冒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真令人作嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人連碰都不想碰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖被這些孩子們打敗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人偶都重返死界了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過這積屍氣冥界波（Corpse Underworld Wave）！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬尼戈特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.43,0:22:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我加上「先生」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區青銅小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心我再把你關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼們就閃一邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩莎 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的巨蟹座馬尼戈特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話不好聽 性格也很扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 身手卻好得一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連死之森林 也像是在自己的後花園
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.74,0:24:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是 我覺得馬尼戈特和我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢 THE LOST CANVAS 冥王神話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.17,0:24:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神和棋子
